      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹老西上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00002",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "曲曲弯弯路，重重叠叠山。雁飞不到处，断不了咱处人。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00003",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "我，曹老西。乃山西太谷县人氏。家道殷富，广有银钱。奉了我爹爹之命，贩卖绸缎。来在这洛阳已有三年，并不曾回家。也不知我那我那爹娘同我那老婆孩儿如何？倒叫我常常挂念。昨日遇到两个同乡朋友，他言道此处有一青楼，新买了一位姑娘，名叫陈三两。无论是谁，只要见她一面，就得花银子三两。吾这几天，实实想家，今日带了些金银财宝，要到她那里去逛一逛去，我也开开眼。不免就此走走。（梆子正板）我一日离家园一日深，思想起老婆孩儿好不伤心。在家奉了爹娘命，到洛阳来贸易生意兴隆。昨日里人言道陈氏三两，她本是青楼中美貌佳人。因此上带银两前去观看，到那里我定要散散心。",
      "text_length": 270
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00004",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹老西下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00005",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老鸨子上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00006",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "身在烟花柳巷，搜罗美貌婵娟。迎接王孙公子，一心只图银钱。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00007",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "我，老鸨子的便是。在这洛阳城中，开一座九开间门大窑子。前月里买了一个姑娘，长的倒也不错。只是她不肯修饰打扮，她说要叫她接客，却也不难，见她一面，要银三两。自从她进了我的门，还没有开过张呐。看这几天，连阴大雨。今天也到晴啦。间壁人家吹弹歌唱，十分热闹。唯独我们这院里冷冷清清，连一个人影儿也没有。到门口去望望去。",
      "text_length": 155
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00008",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "走哇！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00009",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹老西上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00010",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "梆子流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "急急忙忙往前奔，不觉来到了一家门。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00011",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老鸨子看曹老西。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00012",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "咳，我说大爷，您哪怎么老不来啦？昨天我还念诵您来着。走走，家里坐吧。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00013",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "你同我亲热的很，你知道我是谁呀？我姓什么？",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00014",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "你姓赵。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00015",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "我不照。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00016",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "你是姓钱。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00017",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "钱倒有的是。你看看金子银子通多得很。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00018",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "你光景是姓孙。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00019",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "你不要胡猜乱猜。我姓曹。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00020",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "不错，是的。你是曹二爷么！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00021",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "不对。我弟兄只有一个。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00022",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "走吧。家里坐着。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00023",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "我来问问你，你同我乱拉近乎，你是个做什么的人呀？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00024",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "我们这儿就是窑子。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00025",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈哈哈哈！这倒巧啦，我今天正想逛窑子。你是个做什么的人呀？",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00026",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "我呀，我就这窑子里头的老板。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00027",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "你就是这铺子里头的掌柜呀？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00028",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "不敢，你老人家请进来吧。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00029",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "你这里是窑子？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00030",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "是的。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00031",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "是，我就同你进去坐坐。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00032",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "大爷请坐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00033",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "你这院里的姑娘都在哪儿藏着？为何不出来呀？",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00034",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "你别忙，待我去叫她们去。我说都来见见！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00035",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老鸨子下。四妓女同上。曹老西看四妓女。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00036",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "我说你们哪一个是陈三两呀？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00037",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四妓女"
      ],
      "text": "懂得逛窑子再来逛，什么陈三两，李四两，真是七担不够，八蛋肏得！",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00038",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四妓女同下。曹老西呆。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00039",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈！真正欺负我们老西，见了面，可就骂起来啦。掌柜的快来！",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00040",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老鸨子上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00041",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "忽听一声唤，急忙到跟前。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00042",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "大爷有什么事呀？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00043",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "你这窑子真真欺生。见了我，刚说了一句话，她们为何就骂起来我啦？",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00044",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "她们不敢呐，必是你能说了犯恶的话啦吧？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00045",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "我就问了她一声：“你们哪一个叫陈三两”，她们就骂起来啦。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00046",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "怪不得，这是你能不在行。待我给你赔个不是吧。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00047",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "你们这里可有一个陈三两没有？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00048",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "陈三两，我们这里倒有此人。但是她见客一面，必须要花三两银子。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00049",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "我要住她，要多少钱？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00050",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老鸨子看曹老西包袱。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00051",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "要是住她也倒容易。我有一件家伙，等我去拿了来。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00052",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老鸨子取斗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00053",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "来吧，这是我们这里的规矩，要能够把斗用银子填满了，你就住她。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00054",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "好。我有银子，待我取出来。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00055",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹老西解包袱取一锭银子掷斗内。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00056",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "满啦。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00057",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "这一锭不够。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00058",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹老西取一锭银子掷斗内。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00059",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "这可是真满啦。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00060",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "早着哪，你别怕花银子。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00061",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "你这个斗真是填不满的坑。我全都给你吧，你看看满不满？",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00062",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "就算满了吧。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00063",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老鸨子转身，曹老西向地上拾。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00064",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "这还有一点银子渣儿呐。待我带起来吧。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00065",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "你老人家在这儿等一等，待我去叫她出来陪你吃酒。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00066",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "对啦。你给我预备好酒，今天我老西是要开开心。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00067",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "知道啦。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00068",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈三两蓬头垢面暗上，坐。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00069",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "我的银子是花了，不知道陈三两长得有多好看。今日同她困觉，真真不枉人生一世。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00070",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹老西转身见陈三两，呆。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00071",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "我说你是谁呀？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00072",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈三两"
      ],
      "text": "奴家陈三两。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00073",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹老西后退。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00074",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "这是陈三两？咳，我曹老西真真晦气，陈三两怎么是这样一个人。咳，银子已经花了，管他这些那些，捞捞本钱再说。来，猜拳喝酒。",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00075",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈三两"
      ],
      "text": "客官呀！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00076",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "陈三两"
      ],
      "text": "家鸡不打团团转，野鸡不打遥天飞。要吃还是家常饭，要穿还是粗布衣。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00077",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀呀呀呀！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00078",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "梆子摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "听一言来甚惨凄，两泪交流洒湿衣。她把好言将我劝，不由我想起了自己妻。叫一声掌柜的你快来吧，",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00079",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "大爷什么事情呀？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00080",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "梆子摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "叫一声掌柜的你听端的。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00081",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "我说大爷，你放着酒不吃，怎么倒哭起来啦？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00082",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "哎哎，我的掌柜的呀！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00083",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "梆子摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "陈三两方才来劝我，倒叫我心中好惨凄。她言道要吃还是家常饭，要穿还是粗布衣。家鸡打得团团转，野鸡不打遥天飞。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00084",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "掌柜的，快把银子还给我，我老西从今以后，再也不敢逛窑子啦。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00085",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "我说大爷，你为什么哭起来啦？她说的也是几句好话。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00086",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "我知道她是好话。是你不知道，我从山西出门的时候，我的母亲曾经教训过我，不叫在外边浪荡逍遥。她对我也说过这几句话来。今天陈三两她也对我说这几句话，我不由得就想起我的老母亲来啦。今天我这不是来逛窑子来啦！",
      "text_length": 100
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00087",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "那么你来做什么来啦？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00088",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "我简直是来听教训来啦。陈三两她竟把我当做她的儿子来教训起来啦吗？掌柜的，你把我的银子快快还了我吧。我老西从今往后，再也不敢逛窑子了。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00089",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "大爷，你能不要伤心啦，我把这酒菜端到我那一间房子里去，请大爷到我房里吃一杯酒，我来陪你，你看好不好？",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00090",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹老西"
      ],
      "text": "你陪我吃酒？好好。看你年纪虽然是大一点儿，倒还风骚得很。没有想到，今天掌柜的也接起客来啦。走，我尝尝你这个老家伙是个什么滋味。",
      "text_length": 63
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00091",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老鸨子"
      ],
      "text": "得啦，别胡说八道，跟着我走吧。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01025005_e00092",
      "play_id": "01025005",
      "scene_id": "01025005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老鸨子拉曹老西同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}